CatDescriptText: Frankie Mae Pace (1905-1989) was a long time activist as the head of the Hill District Community Council.  Here she is standing in front of her offices; sign reads "Pace's Citizen Committee for Hill District Renewal."
TitMainTitle: Frankie Pace standing in front of Pace's Citizen's Committee for Hill District Renewal Office
